===============================================================================
Python bindings for the XenAPI 1.0 
(C) XenSource, Inc. / Ewan Mellor (firstname.lastname@citrix.com)
===============================================================================

The Xen Management API is an interface for remotely configuring and controlling
virtualised guests running on a Xen-enabled host. 

References & specifications:

http://wiki.xensource.com/xenwiki/XenApi
http://docs.vmd.citrix.com/XenServer/5.6.0fp1/1.0/en_gb/api
http://docs.vmd.citrix.com/XenServer/5.6.0fp1/1.0/en_gb/sdk.html
